CannyValley_Landmark_HighNoon.name: Gravestone
CannyValley_Landmark_HighNoon.description: Explore the town of Gravestone and prepare for a high noon duel with the deadliest husk in Canny Valley.
CannyValley_Landmark_HighNoon.completionText: The legendary gunslinger is gone! Stay tuned for more Canny Valley adventures soon.

objectives.description: Battle Legendary Gunslinger Husk in a [UIRating]+ zone, and explore Gravestone.

CannyValley_Landmark_Memorial.name: V
CannyValley_Landmark_Memorial.description: It's time for Ray to say goodbye to an old Friend. Help Penny build a memorial for Dr. Vinderman.
CannyValley_Landmark_Memorial.completionText: Thank you for the monument, Commaner.

objectives.description: Build a Memorial in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Landmark_Welcome.name: Please Hold
CannyValley_Landmark_Welcome.description: Canny Valley, here we come! Get ready to explore the world beyond Plankerton. Can be only completed in Thunder Route 99.
CannyValley_Landmark_Welcome.completionText: What are we waiting for? Let's go explore!

objectives.description: Discover Landmark in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Mechanical_Constructor.name: Just Build
CannyValley_Mechanical_Constructor.description: With all the sharp-shooting husks in Canny Valley, it's time to brush up on combat building. Build 100 structures in a successful mission.
CannyValley_Mechanical_Constructor.completionText: Don't forget to flex those building skills when fighting powerful enemies.

objectives.description: Build Structures in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Reactive_Bases.name: Canny Underground
CannyValley_Reactive_Bases.description: Search the borders of arid zones for underground bunkers. Can be only completed in a desert or Thunder Route 99 zone.
CannyValley_Reactive_Bases.completionText: We need to find out what the survivors in the bunkers were working on.

objectives.description: Search Bunkers in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Reactive_DinoBones.name: The Bones Collector
CannyValley_Reactive_DinoBones.description: Help Dennis collect bones for his latest experiment. Can be only completed in a desert or Thunder Route 99 zone.

objectives.description: Collect Bones in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Reactive_Glyphs.name: Concept Art
CannyValley_Reactive_Glyphs.description: Deploy scanners to scan the mysterious glyphs in mines and caves. Can be only completed in a desert or Thunder Route 99 zone.
CannyValley_Reactive_Glyphs.completionText: If these glyphs can be trusted, this might not be the first appearance of the the storm...

objectives.description: Deploy Scanners in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Reactive_Jukeboxes.name: A Harrowing Journey Of Drumming
CannyValley_Reactive_Jukeboxes.description: Steel Wool needs a new drummer. Destroy jukeboxes for the parts needed to build a new drummer. Most often found in Thunder Route 99 zones.
CannyValley_Reactive_Jukeboxes.completionText: We'd better find Anthony before he finds Gravestone.

objectives.description: Gather parts from destroyed jukeboxes in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Reactive_OilSamples.name: Canny Crude!

CannyValley_Reactive_OilSamples.completionText: There are trace elements of storm corruption in the samples...  That can't be good.

objectives.description: Collect Oil Samples in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Reactive_Periscopes.name: Band Probation

objectives.description: Find Periscopes in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Reactive_RockFormations.completionText: We were, in fact, ready to rock.

objectives.description: Gather Rock Samples in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Reactive_Route99.completionText: We are officially on a road trip!

objectives.description: Visit a diner in a [UIRating]+ zone
Visit a motel in a [UIRating]+ zone
Visit a gas station in a [UIRating]+ zone
Visit a truck stop in a [UIRating]+ zone

objectives.description: Search Cars in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Reactive_SeeBot.name: See You Later

objectives.description: Update SEE-bot in a [UIRating]+ zone

objectives.description: Search Servers in a [UIRating]+ zone

CannyValley_Reactive_Survey.name: What Are Names?
CannyValley_Reactive_Survey.description: Follow the trail of survey equipment to find Lars' former bandmate, Syd. Can be only completed in a desert or Thunder Route 99 zone.
CannyValley_Reactive_Survey.completionText: It's Syd! Weâ€™re getting this band back together!

objectives.description: Find Survey Equipment in a [UIRating]+ zone

objectives.description: Collect Songbooks in a [UIRating]+ zone

objectives.description: Find Trail Posts in a [UIRating]+ zone

objectives.description: Collect Tumbleweed Movement Data in a [UIRating]+ zone

Search the area for eyewitness accounts of Ayers' reign of terror. Look for old watertowers and windmills. Can be only completed in a desert or Thunder Route 99 zone.

ElderQuest_BattleTheHorde_1.name: Tele-Fortation
ElderQuest_BattleTheHorde_1.description:
Now it's time for you and your team to defend your deployable bases and eradicate the enemy!

Make sure you build weapons, ammo, and traps! You don't have much time or resources!

Once you're ready, access the Control Panel, select Tier 7 or higher difficulty, and let the battle begin!
ElderQuest_BattleTheHorde_1.completionText: The enemies have been defeated! Excellent job!

objectives.description: Complete a Tier 7 (or higher) of Operation Block Party

ElderQuest_BuildDeployableBase.name: Base in the Box
ElderQuest_BuildDeployableBase.description:
The husks are plotting a large scale assault, and we need to take them by surprise.

Join up with other Commanders, build a base you can deploy to designated zones, and battle!
ElderQuest_BuildDeployableBase.completionText: Deployable base built and ready for battle!

objectives.description: Build a Deployable Base in Operation Block Party with 10 or more structures

ElderQuest_ElderUnlock.name: Operation Block Party (Unlock)
ElderQuest_ElderUnlock.description:
Commander, your squad has done a great job in Stonewood battling husks and saving survivors. However, Operation Block Party needs your immediate attention! 

To unlock Operation Block Party: 
Select the Skills tab
Select the Operation Block Party skill node
Select purchase to unlock the skill node

objectives.description: Unlock Operation Block Party Skill Tree Node

BlockbusterQuest_2018_OpenCaches_Repeata.name: Fortune and Glory
BlockbusterQuest_2018_OpenCaches_Repeata.description:
Now that you have access to a Perk Recombobulator, open as many caches as you can to earn PERK-UPs to power it. You can find caches in the world by killing Mini-Bosses or looting valuable treasure chests. Note: This is a repeatable Quest.

The Perk Recombobulator feature is available after completing the Plankerton Storm Shield Defense 2 Quest.

objectives.description: Open 10 Caches

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Barrels.name: Ooze Control
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Barrels.description: Spitfire is missing, and toxic waste barrels are popping up in unexpected places. Search the barrels and discover the connection.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Barrels.completionText: Spitfire needs our help. We have to find a way to bring him home without endangering everyone in Homebase.

objectives.description: Search Barrels

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Bees.name: The Powers That Bee
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Bees.description: Some heroes aren't born, they're made. Eliminate Bee Hive husks and collect corrupted beehive pieces for Lok's super experiment.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Bees.completionText: No bees were harmed in the completion of this quest.

objectives.description: Eliminate Beehive Husks And Collect Corrupted Beehive Pieces.

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Broadcast.name: We Interrupt This Broadcast...
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Broadcast.description: The TVs around the world are broadcasting ominous messages. We need to investigate - destroy the TVs and collect corrupted receivers to understand what is happening. Something is corrupting the receivers, but it is not the storm. TVs are most often found in Suburban and Urban zones.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Broadcast.completionText: The broadcasts seem to be coming from the meteoriteâ€¦ and theyâ€™re getting stronger.

objectives.description: Collect Television Receivers

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_CarbonDat.name: Carbon Dating
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_CarbonDat.description: We should check to see if the chrome husks are from the future. Just to be sure. Collect a sample for carbon dating.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_CarbonDat.completionText: The carbon dating results are inconclusive. Dennis might actually be right.

objectives.description: Collect Sample

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_ChromeHus.name: Sometimes They Come Back
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_ChromeHus.description: We've got new monsters! Take out Chrome Husks and collect samples for analysis.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_ChromeHus.completionText: The results are in! Chrome Husks have a weakness to fire, and ice elemental weapons and traps.

objectives.description: Collect Chrome Husk Data

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Clocks.name: Handshake
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Clocks.description: Help Dennis prove the existence of time skips by collecting clock parts. Clocks are most often found in Urban and Suburban zones.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Clocks.completionText: It turns out a lot of things move in an earthquake, Dennis.

objectives.description: Collect Clocks

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_CometShar.name: It Came From Space!
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_CometShar.description: We should probably investigate that massive explosion. Search the zone for any signs of the meteorite.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_CometShar.completionText: Bad news! The meteorite shards have destroyed our scanning equipment. Be careful out there.

objectives.description: Collect Meteorite Shards

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Consoles.name: Project Tailor
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Consoles.description: The cure for Spitfireâ€™s illness may be hidden in the Vindertech archives. Help Ray track down audio logs related to Vindertechâ€™s first armored suit prototype. Look for system terminals in Industrial zones.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Consoles.completionText: The Project Tailor audio logs should help us design a suit powerful enough to withstand meteorite corrosion.

objectives.description: Find Project Tailor Files

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Cows.name: I Have No Voice and I Must Moo
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Cows.description: Lok isnâ€™t ready to lead the way, but he still deserves a voice. Collect farm sounds to give him the voice pack of his dreams.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Cows.completionText: Moo. Moo moo moo moo? Moo.

objectives.description: Collect Farm Sounds

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_DeployCBo.name: Look Out!
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_DeployCBo.description: We canâ€™t destroy a meteorite without lasers, and we canâ€™t make lasers without glass, so thereâ€™s only one solution. Search for lightning glass by deploying SEE-bots in lightning rich environments.

objectives.description: Deploy SEE-bots

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Earthquak.name: Earthquakes!
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Earthquak.description: Is it just me, or have there been a lot of unexplained earthquakes since the meteorite landed? We should probably look into that. Deploy remote seismographs, and Iâ€™ll analyze the data.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Earthquak.completionText: Iâ€™ve crunched the numbers and not only is it 995% more earthquakey than usual, itâ€™s getting worse by the day. Hmm...

objectives.description: Deploy Remote Seismographs

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Fans.name: Bee Gone
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Fans.description: Help Ray collect fans to clear the bees from Homebase. Found inside houses and buildings.

objectives.description: Collect Fans

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Flyers.name: Super Flyers
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Flyers.description: You can't battle a mysterious space rock without a team of super-powered superheroes! Let's let the superhero community know we're recruiting!

objectives.description: Launch Flyers

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_JulyFourt.name: Independence Day
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_JulyFourt.description: Celebrate the independence of our Home Base with a display of festive fireworks!

objectives.description: Launch Fireworks

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Magnets.name: Magnets!
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Magnets.description: The Cloaked Star might have a solution for the Chrome Husk infestation. Stand by to deploy magnetic snares!
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Magnets.completionText: Weâ€™ll have the chrome husk infestation under control in no time.

objectives.description: Deploy Magnetic Snares

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mailboxes.name: Post Credits
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mailboxes.description: Replies are piling up from Lok's superhero job posting. Search mailboxes to find a true hero.

objectives.description: Search Mailboxes

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mattresse.name: Sleep On It
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mattresse.description: We've saved so many survivors we're running out of beds. Search the area for suitable mattresses. Beds are mostly found in Suburban and Urban zones.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mattresse.completionText: Sleep tight, donâ€™t the the husk horde bite.

objectives.description: Collect Mattresses

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mayhem.name: Renegade Rampage
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mayhem.description: It looks like there's a new vigilante in town. Follow the path of destruction and search for clues for the vigilante's identity.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mayhem.completionText: Sure heâ€™s a loose cannon, and his methods might be a bit unorthodox, but weâ€™ve got to get this guy on our team.

objectives.description: Follow The Trail Of Destruction

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_PortaPott.name: Jack Of All Trades
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_PortaPott.description: Homebase plumbing is crisis waiting to happen. Help Jack collect everything we need to stave off disaster. Look for portable toilets in the Industrial Zones.

objectives.description: Collect Neutralizer Fluid

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_RaySignal.name: Ray Of Hope
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_RaySignal.description: It's time for Lok's reign of terror to come to an end. Deploy searchlights to call Ray back to Homebase.

objectives.description: Deploy Lights

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Rescue.name: Fallen Star
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Rescue.description: Whether he wants it or not, The Cloaked Star needs our help. Search the zone, we need to find him before itâ€™s too late!
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Rescue.completionText: Good rescue. The Cloaked Star is back in Homebase and it looks like heâ€™s going to be okay.

objectives.description: Rescue The Cloaked Star

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Restauran.name: Taste Wizard
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Restauran.description: The Taste Wizard predictive ordering network has been corrupted by the storm. Help Dennis destroy Taste Wizard before it destroys us all. The restaurants are most often found in Urban zones.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Restauran.completionText: It worked! Malicious network activity is declining rapidly.

objectives.description: Upload Dennisâ€™ Order

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_RetrieveC.name: Don't Blink
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_RetrieveC.description: We need glass to build our lasers. Collect SEE-bots to search for evidence of lightning glass.

objectives.description: Collect SEE-bots

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Rubber.name: Ex-Ray
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Rubber.description: We have the Project Tailor plans! Start collecting the materials weâ€™ll need to build the suit as we listen to the audio logs. The high density rubber can be found in Industrial and Urban zones.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Rubber.completionText: Nice work. We almost have everything we need to build the suit.

objectives.description: Collect High Density Rubber

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Scanners.name: Malevolent Presence
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Scanners.description: Deploy scanners to test Dennisâ€™ theory about a rogue network coming online.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Scanners.completionText: The malicious network is somewhere close by. Dennis is standing by to help.

objectives.description: Deploy Scanners

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_ShielderD.name: Ready-to-war
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_ShielderD.description: If we understood more about Shield Husks, weâ€™d be able to improve the shielding in Spitfireâ€™s suit. Collect Shielder Husk data.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_ShielderD.completionText: Yes. It makes so much sense now. The secretâ€¦ is shields.

objectives.description: Collect Shielder Data

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Tankers.name: Blocked!
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Tankers.description: We almost have everything we need to complete Spitfireâ€™s suit. Collect stainless steel as we sort through the last of the Project Tailor audio logs. This quest requires an Industrial zone.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Tankers.completionText: There are no more messages from Desiree, but we have everything we need to build Spitfireâ€™s suit.

objectives.description: Destroy Tank Trucks To Collect Steel

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Tombstone.name: Every Film Bed, Woof!
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Tombstone.description: The Cloaked Star has beenâ€¦ smashing gravestones. We should probably look into that.
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Tombstone.completionText: The Cloaked Star needs our help. We need to find a way to save him from himself.

objectives.description: Search Smashed Gravestones

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Toys.name: Baby Daddy
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Toys.description: Collect stuffed animals to prepare Dennis for the biggest journey of his life. Toys are most often found in Suburban and Urban zones.

objectives.description: Collect Stuffed Animals

BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Trodes.name: Lie to Me
BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Trodes.description: Itâ€™s time to find out if Raven can be trusted. Search the zone for everything we need to build a lie detector. Look for a hospital, which is most likely to be found in the Urban zone.

objectives.description: Collect Testing Equipment

Bot_Fetch_Quest_A1.name: Lone Wolf-bot
Bot_Fetch_Quest_A1.description: With the rest of the Homebase Crew joining the fight, Ray faces a difficult choice.

objectives.description: Collect movies

Bot_Fetch_Quest_A2.name: No Cameras Please
Bot_Fetch_Quest_A2.description: Ray's ready to take her first step into battle, but it's not going to be pretty.

objectives.description: Deactivate surveillance cameras

Bot_ReactiveKill_Quest_A3.name: Ray-Bot Rampage
Bot_ReactiveKill_Quest_A3.description: Take cover! Ray-Bot is armed, dangerous, and ready for action.

objectives.description: Eliminate Husks

Brainstorm_Quest_A01_Gather.name: A Dark and Brainstormy Night
Brainstorm_Quest_A01_Gather.description: The Door to Darkness is re-opening. Willow needs your help investigating who or what's behind it!

objectives.description: Search the Haunted Hotel for clues

Brainstorm_Quest_A02_Eliminate.name: Don't Quoth Me
Brainstorm_Quest_A02_Eliminate.description: Lars leads the team into zombie chicken combat with a spooky story.

objectives.description: Eliminate Zombie Chickens in Hexsylvania.

Brainstorm_Quest_A03_Fetch.name: Well Well Well...
Brainstorm_Quest_A03_Fetch.description: After falling into a well, Dennis must come to terms with his greatest fears.

objectives.description: Search wells in Hexsylvania and eliminate Takers.

Brainstorm_Quest_A04_Deliver.name: Girlbossurtunity
Brainstorm_Quest_A04_Deliver.description: Those last stories were childâ€™s play. Sarahâ€™s got a REAL scary story to share.

objectives.description: Deliver boxes of loungewear to unsuspecting citizens.

Brainstorm_Quest_A05_Fetch.name: The Heat of Paddle
Brainstorm_Quest_A05_Fetch.description: Spooky stories can always be improved with a campfire! Hint: Best found in Haunted Forest or Swamp zones. Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

objectives.description: Light 6 Campfires

Brainstorm_Quest_A06_Destroy.name: It's All Gravey
Brainstorm_Quest_A06_Destroy.description: Discover Willow's greatest fear by helping her track down and destroy some ominously named tombstones...

objectives.description: Destroy Tombstones

Brainstorm_Quest_A07_Landmark.name: Jar-Related Consequences
Brainstorm_Quest_A07_Landmark.description: Foil Brainstorm's spooky plan by battling the Door to Darkness!

objectives.description: Fight through the haunted hotel basement.

Brainstorm_Quest_A08_Fetch.name: Fill 'er Up
Brainstorm_Quest_A08_Fetch.description: Refresh Brainstormâ€™s brine and return him to his normal brain monster state.

objectives.description: Gather new Brain Brine from lab equipment.

HordeQuest_BuildBase.completionText: With this brand spanking new Deployable fort, you're ready to Challenge the Horde!

Fennix_Quest_A01_BuildRadarTowers.name: Rebuilding
Fennix_Quest_A01_BuildRadarTowers.description: Homebase needs to rebuild after a recent unfortunate series of events. Build radar towers in any mission to fix the radar network.

objectives.description: Build radar towers.

Fennix_Quest_A02_Eliminate.name: Evaluation Period
Fennix_Quest_A02_Eliminate.description: Fennix wants to know what he's working with. Show him how it's done and eliminate husks in any mission!

objectives.description: Eliminate husks.

Fennix_Quest_A03_RescueSurvivors.name: Survey Says...
Fennix_Quest_A03_RescueSurvivors.description: Fennix needs to learn what the people think of Homebase. Rescue survivors in any mission and poll their opinions.

objectives.description: Rescue and interview survivors.

Fennix_Quest_A04_Fetch.name: Rebranding
Fennix_Quest_A04_Fetch.description: Deliver fliers to survivors to inform them of Homebase's new brand. Mailboxes are commonly found in Suburban and City zones.

objectives.description: Deliver fliers to survivors.

Fennix_Quest_A05_Complete.name: We've Been Robbed!
Fennix_Quest_A05_Complete.description: Complete a Ride the Lightning mission to help Lars gather info on Fennix's location.

objectives.description: Complete a Ride the Lightning mission.

Fennix_Quest_A06_Fetch.name: The Fox Hunt
Fennix_Quest_A06_Fetch.description: Fennix has robbed Homebase. Use the FOX-SEE-BOT to locate where he has run off to.

objectives.description: Use FOX-SEE-BOT to locate Fennix.

Fennix_Quest_A07_DestroyEncampments.name: To Trust a Fox
Fennix_Quest_A07_DestroyEncampments.description: Clear encampments in any mission while Homebase decides what to do with the trickster.

objectives.description: Clear Husk Encampments

FirstStormQuest_CannyDiff_CompleteStormZ.name: Mutant Storms
FirstStormQuest_CannyDiff_CompleteStormZ.description: Storms are rapidly spreading. Look at all that purple turbulance on the map! Complete some missions in those hexes.

objectives.description: Complete 10 Mutant Storm missions in a [UIRating]+ zone

FirstStormQuest_CompleteStormZones.name: Storm Alert!
FirstStormQuest_CompleteStormZones.description: Storms are rapidly spreading. Look at all that purple turbulance on the map! Complete some missions in those hexes.

objectives.description: Complete 10 Mutant Storm missions

FirstStormQuest_Evolve_Hydraulic.name: Hydraulic Weapon Evolution
FirstStormQuest_Evolve_Hydraulic.description: Visit the Armory tab to evolve a Hydraulic Weapon of your choice. Evolved Weapons are more powerful and may require rare crafting ingredients.

objectives.description: Evolve a Hydraulic Weapon by 1 Star

FirstStormQuest_HydraulicStormLlama.name: Form of... Llama!
FirstStormQuest_HydraulicStormLlama.description: Survive the Storm and earn your very own Storm Llama. Earn Storm Tickets by successfully completing missions in Mutant Storm missions. You can also earn Storm Tickets by completing Survive the Storm missions.

objectives.description: Purchase a Storm Llama from the Loot tab

FirstStormQuest_KillEnragedHusks.name: Enraged
FirstStormQuest_KillEnragedHusks.description: Commander, watch out! These husks are mutated by the storm. Eliminate as many of them as you can!

objectives.description: Eliminate 1500 Enraged Husks in Mutant Storm missions

Visit the Command tab to assign your Heroes on an Expedition.
After an Expedition has been completed, go back to the Expeditions Squads tab and see if it was successful!

Commander, you may want to consider retiring more of your heroes, personnel, and schematics to your Collection Book. If you can level up your Collection Book to 30, you will receive additional scavenger rewards!

objectives.description: Destroy Barrels of Poisoned Punch in Scurvy Shoals

objectives.description: Find Boomboxes in Scurvy Shoals

objectives.description: Gather 8 VHS tapes

BetaStormQuest_CompleteBetaStorms_Repeat.name: Beta Storm Prospecting
BetaStormQuest_CompleteBetaStorms_Repeat.description: We're seeing some strange weather patterns in the area. Complete some Beta Storm missions, for Science (and Gold)!

objectives.description: Complete 2 Beta Storm missions

LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Boxes.name: Oh!
LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Boxes.description: Kyle and Eagle Eye are in love... but they have nothing in common. Search for something, anything they can agree on.

objectives.description: Search for Stuff

LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Chests.name: Maps
LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Chests.description: The antidote to love lies in Hexsylvania... how do we get there again?

objectives.description: Search Hexsylvanian Travel Chests

LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Decanters.name: I Remember Me
LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Decanters.description: It's time to put an end to the love storm. Distribute Hate Potion to the love scrambled heroes of Homebase.

objectives.description: Distribute Hate Potions

LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Phones.name: Love Wars
LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Phones.description: Find out who is behind the terrible new advice call in show, Dennis The Love King.

objectives.description: Find Working Payphones in Urban and Suburban zones

LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Sensors.name: Satellite of Love
LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Sensors.description: The forecast calls for crushing infatuation! Help Lars track the love storm.

objectives.description: Deploy Sensors for Lars

LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Teddys.name: Happy Together
LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Teddys.description: Last year's teddy bear balloons are causing problems for the local wildlife, track 'em down and bring 'em home.

objectives.description: Collect Deflated Teddy Bear Balloons

LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Telescopes.name: Little Star
LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_Telescopes.description: A love fog is settling over Homebase. Help Sarah look to the stars to find her love horoscope.

objectives.description: Deploy Telescopes

LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_VHS.name: I Think I Need a New Heart
LoveQuest_2019_Fetch_VHS.description: Ray just isn't feeling the love. Find some romantic comedies to set the mood for romance.

objectives.description: Find Romantic Comedies

LoveQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Containers.name: Trapped by Love
LoveQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Containers.description: Penny has a new plan for dealing with the husk horde. Collect container walls...

objectives.description: Collect Container Walls in Industrial zones

LoveQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Mailboxes.name: Uh Oh, Love Comes to Town
LoveQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Mailboxes.description: Everyone's in love - in a bad way. Search love letters for clues.

objectives.description: Collect Love Letters from Mailboxes

LoveQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Mushrooms.name: Papers
LoveQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Mushrooms.description: Sarah and Jonesy have returned from Hexslyvania with the Hate Potion recipe. Collect hate mushrooms and get ready to brew!

objectives.description: Collect Hate Mushrooms in Forest zones

LoveQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Newspapers.name: Pictures of You
LoveQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Newspapers.description: The Cloaked Star refuses the call of romance. Help him come to terms with the past in a newspaper box smashing trip down memory lane.

objectives.description: Collect Old Newspapers in Urban and Suburban zones

LoveQuest_2019_GatherCollect_OfficeStuff.name: The Book of Love
LoveQuest_2019_GatherCollect_OfficeStuff.description: Director Riggs needs a love policy stat! Search office spaces for any love related HR guidelines.

objectives.description: Collect Old HR Guidelines from Office File Cabinets and Cubicles in Urban, Suburban, Industrial zones

LoveQuest_2019_KillCollect_LoveLobbers.name: All My Friends
LoveQuest_2019_KillCollect_LoveLobbers.description: We found the cure, but the love lobbers are still lobbing. Take 'em out, collect their Love Poison, and tell 'em how you feel.

objectives.description: Collect Love Poison Bottles from Love Lobbers

LoveQuest_2019_Landmark_Trebuchet.name: You Send Me
LoveQuest_2019_Landmark_Trebuchet.description: Prepare to send an expedition to Hexsylvania, trebuchet style.

objectives.description: Prepare the Trebuchet

PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Banners.name: Under the Black Flag
PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Banners.description: Teach our pirate recruits the secrets of piratical intimidation by planting pirate flags.

objectives.description: Deploy Pirate Flags in any zone

PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Bottles.name: Bottled Memoranda
PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Bottles.description: Check in on Blakebeard and Keelhaul's adventures on the high seas by collecting bottled messages.

objectives.description: Collect Messages from bottles

PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Lighthouses.name: Light the Way
PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Lighthouses.description: Light stone beacons to continue the search for Rowdy Jack's treasure.

objectives.description: Light the Stone Beacons

PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Mounds.name: Another Man's Treasure
PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Mounds.description: Dig up everything Blakebeard and Keelhaul have stolen from Homebase.

objectives.description: Find Caches in any zone

PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_SeeBots.name: SEE-Wolf
PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_SeeBots.description: A black flag flies on the horizon, are pirates headed for Homebase? Stand by to deploy our state of the art pirate detection system.

objectives.description: Deploy PIRA-SEE-Bots in any zone

PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Shanties.name: You Shant
PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Shanties.description: Help Blakebeard and Keelhaul rekindle their sea spirit by finding the perfect shanty.

objectives.description: Search for Sea Shanties

PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Statues.name: Stone Faced
PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Statues.description: The treasure hunt is on! Search ancient Plankenesian stone heads for clues.

objectives.description: Search Ancient Plankenesian Stone Heads for clues

PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Treasure.name: No One Leaves!
PirateQuest_2019_Fetch_Treasure.description: This is it! Search the zone to find Rowdy Jack's treasure.

objectives.description: Find the Treasure. You might find it in any zone

PirateQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Chairs.name: One Step
PirateQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Chairs.description: Blakebeard and Keelhaul may not need peg legs yet, but it never hurts to be prepared. Destroy wooden chairs to harvest peg legs.

objectives.description: Collect Peg Legs from most wooden chairs.

PirateQuest_2019_GatherCollect_GrillPart.name: A Celebration of the Sea
PirateQuest_2019_GatherCollect_GrillPart.description: Fate has called upon Dennis to craft the ultimate Pirate Burger, but is he ready for the challenge?

objectives.description: Collect Grill Parts for Dennis. Found mostly in Suburban and Lakeside zones.

PirateQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Swings.name: Climb Aboard!
PirateQuest_2019_GatherCollect_Swings.description: Help Director Riggs build a sea sickness cure for Blakebeard and Keelhaul. HINT: Springs and Swing Parts can be found in Suburban zones.

objectives.description: Gather springs and swing parts to construct a sea-sickness simulator.

PIrateQuest_2019_KillCollect_Melee.name: Abordage
PIrateQuest_2019_KillCollect_Melee.description: Grab a melee weapon and prepare to demonstrate your swashbuckling, husk busting skills.

objectives.description: Collect Melee Trophies from husks

PIrateQuest_2019_KillCollect_MistMonster.name: Ship Wrecked
PIrateQuest_2019_KillCollect_MistMonster.description: Don't let the mist monsters make off with Blakebeard and Keelhaul's pirate ship!

objectives.description: Find Ship Parts by eliminating mist monsters in any zone.

PirateQuest_2019_Landmark_Island.name: Yarrr!
PirateQuest_2019_Landmark_Island.description: The pirates have crashed! Let's disarm their ship before they have a chance to attack.

objectives.description: Neutralize the Pirate Threat

PirateQuest_2019_Landmark_WalkThePlank.name: Walk the Plank
PirateQuest_2019_Landmark_WalkThePlank.description: Our pirates are ready to take to the seas once more. Help Blakebeard and Keelhaul build the pirate ship of their dreams.

objectives.description: Build the Pirate Ship

S12_DanceEmote_Quest_A6.name: I'm Only Dancing
S12_DanceEmote_Quest_A6.description: Ray wants to convince Homebase that love is worth the risk. The best way to accomplish this is to dance! Hint: Use a dance emote at the marked locations in the area.

objectives.description: Dance at marked dance locations

S12_Fetch_Quest_A2.name: Disco Demolition
S12_Fetch_Quest_A2.description: Ray has convinced Farrah to not destroy Homebase's capacity for love, instead they are going to destroy dance floors.

objectives.description: Place devices to destroy dance floors

S12_Fetch_Quest_A3.name: Loveless
S12_Fetch_Quest_A3.description: Farrah has commissioned Lars to write a song which captures the anti-love spirit. Help by finding boxes of break-up materials to inspire the musician.

objectives.description: Find boxes of anti-love memorabilia

S12_Fetch_Quest_A4.name: Songs of Hate and Hate
S12_Fetch_Quest_A4.description: Lars is ready to debut his newest song inspired by the tragic break ups found in the discarded boxes. Deploy speakers in the area to blast the somber tune.

objectives.description: Deploy speakers to play Lars' new song

S12_Fetch_Quest_A5.name: Forbidden Love
S12_Fetch_Quest_A5.description: Major Oswald isn't giving up on his mission. Help spread anti-love propaganda by deploying flyer cannons.

objectives.description: Deploy flyer cannons to spread anti-love propaganda

S12_GatherCollect_Quest_A1.name: You're No Good
S12_GatherCollect_Quest_A1.description: Major Oswald has enlisted the help of Farrah to stop the spread of love. Her first suggestion is to deliver disheartening letters to the team of Homebase. Hint: Best found in Urban and Suburban zones.

objectives.description: Destroy mailboxes to collect envelopes

S12_ReactiveKill_Quest_A7.name: Leap of Faith
S12_ReactiveKill_Quest_A7.description: Love is back! The love lobbers are also out in force. Eliminate as many as you can to prevent heartbreak.

objectives.description: Eliminate love lobbers

S12_BuildRadar_Quest_B7.name: Your Own Boss
S12_BuildRadar_Quest_B7.description: Knox wants to try this "Constructor" thing. Help him by building a radar tower.

objectives.description: Build a radar tower for Knox.

S12_Collect_Quest_B4.name: Why We Fight
S12_Collect_Quest_B4.description: Knox and Lars found survivors near the storm. Get out there and rescue them!

objectives.description: Rescue survivors found by Knox.

S12_Fetch_Quest_B1.name: Henchin'
S12_Fetch_Quest_B1.description: Many personnel files were lost during the latest husk attack. Help the Director find hard copies of the files by searching old filing cabinets and uncover Knox's past.

objectives.description: Search filing cabinets for personnel files on Knox.

S12_Fetch_Quest_B5.name: It's Like A Dare
S12_Fetch_Quest_B5.description: Helping people, not hurting people. Now that the survivors are safe, help Knox gather supplies for them. Basic supplies. Very basic. HINT: Find stacks of toilet paper in bathrooms.

objectives.description: Search abandoned shelters and homes for toilet paper.

S12_GatherCollect_Quest_B2.name: Right In The Zeus
S12_GatherCollect_Quest_B2.description: Knox needs parts from vehicles to fix Lars' van. Help by breaking down abandoned vehicles to find what's needed. HINT: Parts best found in City and Suburb zones.

objectives.description: Gather vehicle parts by destroying vehicles.

S12_KillCollect_Quest_B6.name: The Test
S12_KillCollect_Quest_B6.description: THERAPYBOT has been asked to evaluate Knox, but the answer keys were stolen by husks. Eliminate Pitcher and Zapper husks and recover the answer booklets!

objectives.description: Eliminate Pitcher and Zapper husks to collect answer booklets

S12_ReactiveKill_Quest_B3.name: Hero Training
S12_ReactiveKill_Quest_B3.description: Show Knox what it takes to be a hero. Eliminate Mist Monsters or 'Sploders to show him how its done!

objectives.description: Eliminate Mist Monsters and 'Sploders!

StarlightQuest_Complete_D1_A.name: The Crypts
StarlightQuest_Complete_D1_A.description: The Crypts beckon you to enter and defeat its master! Complete a mission in the Crypts Dungeon to gain access to The Inferno and The Lab!

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Crypts Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D1_B.name: The Crypts pt 2
StarlightQuest_Complete_D1_B.description: The Crypts are certainly a spooky place, but not too spooky for you! Complete two more missions in the Crypts Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete two missions in the Crypts Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D1_C.name: The Crypts pt 3
StarlightQuest_Complete_D1_C.description: Put all of your fears to an eternal rest and conquer The Crypts for good. Complete one final mission in the Crypts Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Crypts Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_Melee_D1.name: The Crypts: Melee Only!
StarlightQuest_Complete_Melee_D1.description: A special Melee Only challenge is available in The Crypts! Complete this challenge to unlock a new Timed Run challenge.

objectives.description: Complete the Melee Only challenge in The Crypts.

StarlightQuest_Complete_Melee_Timed_D1.name: The Crypts: Melee and Timed!
StarlightQuest_Complete_Melee_Timed_D1.description: Complete the Melee Only Timed Run challenge for The Crypts!

objectives.description: Complete the Melee Only, Timed Run challenge in The Crypts.
objectives.hudDescription: Melee Only / Timed Run Crypts completed

StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D1.name: The Crypts: Timed Run!
StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D1.description: Complete The Crypts within the allotted time or face certain doom! Completing this challenge will unlock a Timed Run challenge for Inferno.

objectives.description: Complete the Timed Run challenge in The Crypts.

StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D1.name: Keeper of Crypts (Daily)
StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D1.description:
Pay your respects to an old friend and successfully complete a mission in the Crypts Dungeon.
Note: This is a daily quest.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Crypts Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D2_A.name: Inferno
StarlightQuest_Complete_D2_A.description: Inferno is a dungeon full of lava, fiery husks, and... fun! Complete a mission in the Inferno Dungeon to gain access to the Grotto!

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Inferno Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D2_B.name: Inferno's Revenge
StarlightQuest_Complete_D2_B.description: The deeper you go into the Inferno Dungeon, the hotter it gets. Complete two missions in the Inferno Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete two missions in the Inferno Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D2_C.name: Inferno's Last Stand
StarlightQuest_Complete_D2_C.description: Complete one final mission in the Inferno Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Inferno Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D2.name: Inferno: Timed Run!
StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D2.description: Complete Inferno within the allotted time or face certain doom! Completing this challenge will unlock a Timed Run challenge for The Grotto.

objectives.description: Complete the Timed Run challenge in Inferno.

StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D2.name: Inferno Excursion (Daily)
StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D2.description:
Complete a mission in the Inferno Dungeon.
Note: This is a daily quest.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Inferno Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D3_A.name: The Grotto
StarlightQuest_Complete_D3_A.description: Complete a mission in the Grotto Dungeon to gain access to The Labyrinth.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Grotto Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D3_B.name: The Grotto pt 2
StarlightQuest_Complete_D3_B.description: Take a dip in The Grotto to clear out more husks! Complete two more missions in the Grotto Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete two missions in the Grotto Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D3_C.name: The Grotto pt 3
StarlightQuest_Complete_D3_C.description: Complete one final mission in the Grotto Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Grotto Dungeon.
The Grotto Hard (Hidden)

StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D3.name: The Grotto: Timed Run!
StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D3.description: Complete The Grotto within the allotted time or face certain doom! Completing this challenge will unlock a Timed Run challenge for The Labyrinth.

objectives.description: Complete the Timed Run challenge in The Grotto.

StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D3.name: Gotta Grotto (Daily)
StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D3.description:
Complete a mission in the Grotto Dungeon.
Note: This is a daily quest.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Grotto Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D4_A.name: The Labyrinth
StarlightQuest_Complete_D4_A.description: Donâ€™t lose yourself in the grand halls of The Labyrinth. Complete a mission in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D4_B.name: The Labyrinth pt 2
StarlightQuest_Complete_D4_B.description: This Labyrinth seems to be changing every time we enter itâ€¦ And, are we going in circles? Complete two more missions in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete two missions in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D4_C.name: The Labyrinth pt 3
StarlightQuest_Complete_D4_C.description: Master The Labyrinth! Complete one final mission in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Labyrinth Dungeon.
The Labyrinth Hard (Hidden)

StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D4.name: The Labyrinth: Timed Run!
StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D4.description: Complete The Labyrinth within the allotted time or face certain doom! Completing this challenge will unlock a special Melee Only Timed Run challenge for The Crypts.

objectives.description: Complete the Timed Run challenge in The Labyrinth.

StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D4.name: Labyrinthian Lamentation (Daily)
StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D4.description:
Descend again into the Labyrinth! Complete a mission in the Labyrinth dungeon.
Note: This is a daily quest.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_A.name: The Lab
StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_A.description: The Lab has been discovered! Enter if you dare! Complete a mission in the Lab Dungeon!

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Lab Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_B.name: The Lab pt 2
StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_B.description: The Lab is a perilous place, but you're not afraid! Complete two more missions in the Lab Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete two missions in the Lab Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_C.name: The Lab pt 3
StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_C.description: Complete one final mission in the Lab Dungeon.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Lab Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_Hard.name: Lab Expert
StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_Hard.description: Complete the Lab at the most challenging level.

objectives.description: Complete the Lab Dungeon in a [UIRating]+ zone.

StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D5Science.name: Return to the Lab (Daily)
StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D5Science.description:
Complete a mission in the Lab dungeon.
Note: This is a daily quest.

objectives.description: Complete a mission in the Lab Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_All.name: Dungeoneer
StarlightQuest_Complete_All.description: Complete the following Dungeons: The Crypts, Inferno, The Grotto, and The Labyrinth.

objectives.description: Complete the Crypts Dungeon.
Complete the Inferno Dungeon.
Complete the Grotto Dungeon.
Complete the Labyrinth Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Complete_All_Hard.name: Dungeon Champion
StarlightQuest_Complete_All_Hard.description: Complete the following Dungeons at the most challenging level: The Crypts, Inferno, The Grotto, and The Labyrinth.

objectives.description: Complete the Crypts Dungeon in a [UIRating]+ zone.
Complete the Inferno Dungeon in a [UIRating]+ zone.
Complete the Grotto Dungeon in a [UIRating]+ zone.
Complete the Labyrinth Dungeon in a [UIRating]+ zone.

StarlightQuest_Complete_Dailies_1.name: Daily Dungeon Expert
StarlightQuest_Complete_Dailies_1.description: A dungeon a day keeps the Husks at bay... Successfully complete 3 Daily Dungeon quests and start your quest to become a Daily Dungeon Destroyer!

objectives.description: Complete 3 Daily Dungeon quests.

StarlightQuest_Complete_Dailies_2.name: Daily Dungeon Pro
StarlightQuest_Complete_Dailies_2.description: Dungeon clearing is a major part of a balanced daily nutritional plan. Successfully complete 6 total Daily Dungeon quests and further your quest to become a Daily Dungeon Destroyer!

objectives.description: Complete 6 Daily Dungeon quests.

StarlightQuest_Complete_Dailies_3.name: Daily Dungeon Destroyer
StarlightQuest_Complete_Dailies_3.description: The final test of your dedication to Dungeon destruction! Successfully complete 10 total Daily Dungeon quests to finally become a Daily Dungeon Destroyer!

objectives.description: Complete 10 Daily Dungeon quests.

StarlightQuest_Destroy_Urns.name: Urn Your Keep
StarlightQuest_Destroy_Urns.description:
Smash as many spooky urns as you can in successful missions in the Dungeons. Thereâ€™s gotta be valuables hidden within them!
Note: This is a repeatable quest.

objectives.description: Destroy 100 urns in Dungeon missions.

StarlightQuest_DestructibleSpawners.name: Destroy the Source
StarlightQuest_DestructibleSpawners.description: Husks are emerging from odd crystalline objects in the Dungeons. Destroy many of these in successful Dungeon missions to stop the onslaught.

objectives.description: Destroy 6 Husk Monoliths in Dungeon missions.

StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Constructor.name: Dungeoneers: Constructor
StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Constructor.description: Complete any Dungeon as a Constructor.

objectives.description: As a Constructor, successfully clear a Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Ninja.name: Dungeoneers: Ninja
StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Ninja.description: Complete any Dungeon as a Ninja.

objectives.description: As a Ninja, successfully clear a Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Outlander.name: Dungeoneers: Outlander
StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Outlander.description: Complete any Dungeon as an Outlander.

objectives.description: As an Outlander, successfully clear a Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Soldier.name: Dungeoneers: Soldier
StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Soldier.description: Complete any Dungeon as a Soldier.

objectives.description: As a Soldier, successfully clear a Dungeon.

StarlightQuest_FiniteSpawners.name: Rift Reduction
StarlightQuest_FiniteSpawners.description: Storm Rifts are appearing in the Dungeons and Husks are popping out in swarms! Eliminate Husks to deplete the rifts in successful Dungeon missions.

objectives.description: Deplete 6 Dungeon Rifts in Dungeon missions.

StarlightQuest_Kill_Mimics.name: Dungeon Treasure?
StarlightQuest_Kill_Mimics.description: There is a ton of treasure to find in the Dungeons! But, it looks like not all of it is willing to go peacefully. Eliminate Mimics in successful Dungeon missions.

objectives.description: Eliminate 5 Mimics in successful Dungeon missions.

StarlightQuest_Kill_Minibosses.name: Exorcism by Elimination
StarlightQuest_Kill_Minibosses.description:
Eliminate powerful Mini-Bosses in successful Dungeon missions. Doctors say "exorcising" is important for your health!
Note: This is a repeatable quest.

objectives.description: Eliminate 5 Mini-Bosses in Dungeon missions.

StarlightQuest_TrapTrial.name: Dungeon Trap Trial
StarlightQuest_TrapTrial.description: Looks like some evil force acting against you has set up traps that can be seen with spooky glyphs. Become affected by each one of these new traps, for science!

objectives.description: Get hit by an Arrow Dungeon Trap.
Get snared by a Snare Dungeon Trap.
Get hit by a Ceiling Drop Dungeon Trap.
Get teleported by a Teleport Dungeon Trap.

StormQuest_2018_CompleteStormZones_Repea.name: Endless Storms
StormQuest_2018_CompleteStormZones_Repea.description: Storms are rapidly spreading. Look at all that purple turbulance on the map! Complete some missions in those hexes. Note: This is a repeatable Quest.

objectives.description: Complete 2 Mutant Storm missions

StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurvive7Day_D1.name: Against All Odds
StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurvive7Day_D1.description:
Survive the Storm for 7 days in a Power 15 zone.

You can access Survive the Storm by selecting the Map tab and then selecting the Survive the Storm pin.

objectives.description: Complete a 7 Day Survive the Storm in a [UIRating] zone

StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurvive7Day_D2.name: The Will to Survive
StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurvive7Day_D2.description:
Survive a 7 Day mission in a Power 40 zone.

You can access Survive the Storm by selecting the Map tab and then selecting the Survive the Storm pin.

objectives.description: Complete a 7 Day Survive the Storm in a [UIRating] zone

StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurvive7Day_D3.name: Only the Strong Survive
StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurvive7Day_D3.description:
A 7 Day mission in a Power 70 zone? Can you survive?

You can access Survive the Storm by selecting the Map tab and then selecting the Survive the Storm pin.

objectives.description: Complete a 7 Day Survive the Storm in a [UIRating] zone

StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurviveAny.name: Into The Storm
StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurviveAny.description:
Successfully complete Survive the Storm missions in any threat level.

You can access Survive the Storm by selecting the Map tab and then selecting the Survive the Storm pin.
StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurviveAny.completionText: You live to fight another day!

objectives.description: Complete 3 Survive the Storm missions

StormQuest_2018_Landmark_Lars.name: Steel Icarus
StormQuest_2018_Landmark_Lars.description: Launch Lars deep into the storm!

objectives.description: Launch Lars beyond the wall of clouds

StormQuest_2018_Landmark_Observe.name: Reunion Tour
StormQuest_2018_Landmark_Observe.description: It's time to finish Carlos' research! Protect the telescope array until the results come in!
StormQuest_2018_Landmark_Observe.completionText: The data is coming in, and rumors of a Steel Wool reunion are flying, nice work!

objectives.description: Defend the telescope array (4 telescopes) while they are observing the sky

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_ACParts.name: Cleverboards
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_ACParts.description: Commander, I have come up with a foolproof hoverboard based plan to track Carlos down! The only problem is, these hoverboards are idiots! I need your help. Searching rooftops for AC units should help us find the parts we need. Found in Urban, Suburban and Industrial zones.
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_ACParts.completionText: No time to brief the hoverboards! Let's get moving!

objectives.description: Gather AC control circuits from AC units for the Smart Hoverboards

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Equipment.name: Last Known Position
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Equipment.description: Lars has asked us not to search for Carlos. So let's play it cool... as we search the rooftops for Carlos' research equipment. Found mostly in Urban, Suburban and Industrial zones.
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Equipment.completionText: Carlos was last seen in the Southwest near Thunder Route 99.

objectives.description: Find and interact with the research equipment someone's been installing on the rooftops

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Hoverboards.name: Hover Over Yonder
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Hoverboards.description: We don't have time to train the hoverfleet, but I think they'll figure it out. Head out and launch those brilliant boards!
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Hoverboards.completionText: The fleet is hovering off into the unknown!

objectives.description: Deploy smart hoverboards on their journey

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_HuskData.name: Its What's Inside That Counts
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_HuskData.description: We need husk data... the gross kind of husk data. So take no prisoners and collect all samples!
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_HuskData.completionText: Hmm. Tests conclude there's nothing remarkable about this husk slurry you collected. That's strange...

objectives.description: Eliminate and collect mist monster data

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Insulators.name: Iron Van
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Insulators.description: Lars is not going to like it, but we need to upgrade his van for the journey into the storm.Gather the insulators from electrical transformers. Found mostly in Industrial zones.

objectives.description: Find insulators from power transformers around the world

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Maps.name: Oh, Wait. Maps!
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Maps.description: If we're going to head out west, we'll need maps. Search the industrial zone for vehicles likely to have maps. Trucks are easiest to find in Industrial zones.

objectives.description: Gather maps from Trucks and RVs

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Payphones.name: What's A Payphone?
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Payphones.description: The Hover Fleet is calling back! Track down payphones to collect their reports. Found in Urban, Suburban and Industrial zones.
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Payphones.completionText: Word of advice, never cross a Hover Fleet.

objectives.description: Find public payphones the smart hoverboards are calling and retrieve the data

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Records.name: Liner Notes
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Records.description: Steel Wool mania is sweeping Homebase. Scour the streets for anything Steel Wool related. Found mostly in Urban and Suburban zones.
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Records.completionText: When Lars asks for speakers, you know it's going to get loud.

objectives.description: Look for Steel Wool album records

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Research.name: Deep Cuts
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Research.description: Lars' sensor upgrade is a success, but no one can understand the new data. The answer to this strange data may lie in Lars' past. Search any basements to find Lars' old research. Found in Urban, Suburban and Industrial zones.
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Research.completionText: Lars has the research materials he needs, but more importantly we have our very own Steel Wool album.

objectives.description: Find Lars's old research data

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Servers.name: Van Down!
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Servers.description: Help Lars restore his van's systems by collecting backup data from any server racks you can find. Found mostly in Urban and Industrial zones.
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Servers.completionText: The Van is back in action!

objectives.description: Find server clusters in the world and use them for some number-crunching

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_ServiceCars.name: Breaker! Breaker!
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_ServiceCars.description: Lars' van can't keep up with the strange new developments in the sky. Blast open the Van's doors of perception by collecting encrypted radio components from emergency response vehicles.
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_ServiceCars.completionText: So much purple... but what does it mean?

objectives.description: Destroy firetrucks, police cars and ambulances to retrieve Encrypted Radio parts

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_SkyAtlases.name: Stars, Man.
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_SkyAtlases.description: Lars hasn't slept in days and his vital signs do not look good. Let's check in to see what he needs before he crashes his van. The sky atlases can be found mostly in Urban and Suburban zones.
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_SkyAtlases.completionText: We have mapped the stars! The good ones at least.

objectives.description: Find sky atlas parts by destroying bookshelves

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Speakers.name: Encore
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Speakers.description: Lars is ready to rock. Who are we to stand in the way?
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Speakers.completionText: Lars' old research partner and Steel Wool Bassist might still be alive!

objectives.description: Deploy speakers and blast Steel Wool's greatest hits to repel the storm

StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Telescopes.name: Eye Spy
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Telescopes.description: Lars wants telescopes... I have no idea why. Search for telescope parts and I'll figure our what Lars is up to. Found in Urban, Suburban and Industrial zones.
StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Telescopes.completionText: Time to scope out the world beyond Homebase!

objectives.description: Find broken telescopes that we could use to construct a telescope array

StormKing_Daily_Landmark_Bossfight.name: Kingslayer
StormKing_Daily_Landmark_Bossfight.description: Defeat the Storm King! Are you up for this Daily Challenge?

objectives.description: Defeat the Storm King

StormKing_CheckEmail.name: Storm King Pin
StormKing_CheckEmail.description: Congratulations! You have defeated the Storm King! Check your email over the next several days for information on getting a physical Storm King Pin!

SummerQuest_2019_Complete_All.description: The party was a smash success, take a bow. You deserve it.

objectives.description: Collect boxes of fireworks

objectives.description: Collect pool towels

objectives.description: Collect jugs of water

SummerQuest_2019_Gather_Air_Conditioners.description: The people of Homebase are officially too hot to party! Collect air conditioning parts to chill everyone out.

objectives.description: Harvest air conditioner units to collect their parts

SummerQuest_2019_Harvest_Basketball_Hoop.name: Hit the Hoops
SummerQuest_2019_Harvest_Basketball_Hoop.description: The Twine Bounders are set to take on the Plankerton Smashers in the first annual Homebase Playoffs... we should probably build a court. Collect basketball hoops.  Hint: These are easiest found in suburban missions.

objectives.description: Collect parts from basketball hoops

SummerQuest_2019_Harvest_Lawnmower.name: No Mow
SummerQuest_2019_Harvest_Lawnmower.description: If the world has ended, why are we still mowing the lawn? Letâ€™s destroy all remnants of that ancient chore and harvest their parts! Hint: These are easiest found in suburban missions.

objectives.description: Harvest lawn mower parts

SummerQuest_2019_Kill_200.name: Party Crashers
SummerQuest_2019_Kill_200.description: We've got party crashers! Take 'em out!

objectives.description: Eliminate husks with melee

SummerQuest_2019_Kill_Mist.name: Summer Bummer
SummerQuest_2019_Kill_Mist.description: We have reports of misty party crashers. Take 'em out!

SummerQuest_2019_Kill_Wargames.name: Party Games
SummerQuest_2019_Kill_Wargames.description: Nothing gets a party started like a fun ice breaker. Get the fun started with some Wargames. Access Wargames from the Storm Shield Computer in your Homebase or by assisting other players via Neighborhood Watch.

objectives.description: Complete two Wargames simulations

SummerQuest_2019_Light_Fireworks.name: Light'em Up

objectives.description: Light off the fireworks

SummerQuest_2019_Rescue_Survivors.name: Did We Forget Something?

objectives.description: Rescue survivors

SummerQuest_2019_Search_Ice.name: Make That a COLD Drink

AnniversaryQuest_2019_Complete_Cake_Repe.name: Piece of Cake

HomebaseQuest_CompleteExpedition.name: Expeditions
HomebaseQuest_CompleteExpedition.description:
Well done, Commander! You can now send your Heroes on Expeditions. If an Expedition is successful, you receive rewards! Your Heroes will need People and Vehicles to accompany them. Expeditions take time to complete and are not guaranteed to succeed.

Visit the Command tab to assign your Heroes on an Expedition. After an Expedition has been completed, go back to the Expeditions Squads tab and see if it was successful!

objectives.description: Complete an Expedition

HomebaseQuest_ResearchPurchase.name: Research
HomebaseQuest_ResearchPurchase.description:
Research allows you to upgrade your technologies. These new technologies cost Research Points. You earn Research Points over time. Collect enough Research Points to purchase the Fortitude Research Node.

To unlock the Fortitude Research Node:
Select the Skills tab
Select Research: Tier 1
Select the Fortitude Research node
Select Purchase to unlock the node

objectives.description: Purchase Fortitude Research Node

HomebaseQuest_SlotEMTWorker.name: EMT Worker (Slot)
HomebaseQuest_SlotEMTWorker.description:
Well done, Commander! You have unlocked the first EMT Worker slot. Slotting a Survivor in this slot will increase your Homebase Power.

To assign one of your Survivors to your EMT Squad:
Select the Squads tab
Select the Survivor Squads tab
Select EMT Squad
Select the 1st EMT Worker slot
Select a Survivor to slot

objectives.description: Assign a Survivor to the 1st EMT Squad slot

HomebaseQuest_SlotFireTeamAlphaWorker.name: Fire Team Alpha Worker (Slot)
HomebaseQuest_SlotFireTeamAlphaWorker.description:
Well done, Commander! You have unlocked the first Fire Team Alpha Worker slot. Slotting a Survivor in this slot will increase your Homebase Power.

To assign one of your Survivors to your Fire Team Alpha Squad:
Select the Squads tab
Select the Survivor Squads tab
Select Fire Team Alpha
Select the 1st Fire Team Alpha Worker slot
Select a Survivor to slot

objectives.description: Assign a Survivor to the 1st Fire Team Alpha slot

StonewoodQuest_CloseGate_D1.name: Before and After Science
StonewoodQuest_CloseGate_D1.completionText: We've got lasers! ATLAS Atmospheric Laser schematic obtained!

objectives.description: Complete a Fight the Storm mission

StonewoodQuest_Fetch_DirectorStuff.name: A New Direction
StonewoodQuest_Fetch_DirectorStuff.description: Ray needs help with managing survivors. The Director needs some tools. Search boxes and see what you can retrieve.

objectives.description: Search Boxes in a [UIRating]+ City, Suburban, or Industrial zone

StonewoodQuest_Fetch_ResearchCrates.name: Audition
StonewoodQuest_Fetch_ResearchCrates.description: Lars offers to setup a research lab at homebase. There was some equipment he ordered just before the storm, that never got delivered. We need to retrieve the shipments. This quest can be completed in the City, Suburban and Industrial zones.

objectives.description: Collect Research Equipment in a [UIRating]+ City, Suburban, or Industrial zone

StonewoodQuest_Fetch_StormCalls.name: Kicking and Screaming

objectives.description: Search Garbage Cans for lost items in a [UIRating]+ City, Suburban, or Industrial zone

StonewoodQuest_Fetch_TriangulatingPop.name: Triangulating a Circle
StonewoodQuest_Fetch_TriangulatingPop.description: We need to triangulate Pop's position. See what you can do, Commander!  Try Industrial or Urban Zones!

objectives.description: Deploy Scanners in a [UIRating]+ zone

objectives.description: Save 3 Survivors

objectives.description: Collect Machine Parts in a [UIRating]+ Industrial zone

objectives.description: Search City Zones for Hot Rods in a [UIRating]+ zone

It's time to join up with other Commanders and complete a mission in Stonewood!

This Quest must be completed in Stonewood.

objectives.description: Loot a Treasure Chest in a [UIRating]+ zone

STW_StormKingHard_FirstTakedown.completionText: Storm King Defeated in a Power Level 140+ Zone

objectives.description: Eliminate the Mythic Storm King

STW_StormKingHard_KingMe.name: King Me

objectives.description: Eliminate 2 Epic Mini-Bosses in a 140+ zone
